            <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6">The Code Behind <span class="text-brand-accent">The
                    Commercial</span></h1>
            <p class="text-lg text-brand-muted leading-relaxed">
                While my day job focuses on driving revenue retention and enterprise implementation, my foundation is
                deeply technical.
                This page bridges my commercial portfolio with my raw GitHub output.
